<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV10">
<l>taṉṉuḷēti raitteḻun taraṅkaveṇṭa ṭaṅkaṭal</l>
<l>taṉṉuḷēti raitteḻun taṭaṅkukiṉṟa taṉmaipōl</l>
<l>niṉṉuḷēpi ṟantiṟantu niṟpavun tiripavum</l>
<l>niṉṉuḷēya ṭaṅkukiṉṟa nīrmainiṉka ṇiṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Yours is the nature in which the static and the moving beings</l>
<l>get absorbed in You, being born and dying in You,</l>
<l>Like the nature of the white, spacious ocean which rises, grows,</l>
<l rend="indent">and subsides within itself</l>
<l>with waves that rise and grow in it.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
